	<div data-zesty-id="content:block:6-bcfbdaa6d3-vjj3qs:27:31:0:14">{{block('/-/block/hero_full.html?variant=7-fa9ca1e5d8-8w22kh')}}</div>
	<div class="p-6 rounded-5 bg-light mb-18" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:10:25">
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:10:25-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<h6 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:44">Christmas Center Employment Opportunities</h6>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:74">
	The Salvation Army needs several employees for&nbsp;short-term&nbsp;seasonal employment as part of our Christmas assistance team. Our Angel Tree program will run from&nbsp;<strong>Oct. 2&nbsp;to Dec. 22</strong>&nbsp;and will require several full-time employees to fill these&nbsp;temporary&nbsp;roles. Salaries range from&nbsp;<strong>$15-$17&nbsp;per hour</strong>. Last year we provided Christmas assistance to over 3,500 children and 1,200 seniors in the Charlotte community.&nbsp;If you have a passion for serving others and enjoy the hustle and bustle of Christmas, please apply below for consideration. Interviews will be conducted the week of September 9th&nbsp;and 15th. <strong>NOTE:</strong> these roles are full-time roles with daily hours from 8:30 – 4:30 and some Saturday and evening work required.
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:3:85"><a href="https://www.paycomonline.net/v4/ats/web.php/jobs/ViewJobDetails?job=18808&amp;clientkey=32845297BC28AB21BFFD7C682F3E1551" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Apply Online!</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:4:10"></div>
<div class="btgrid" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:5:81">
	<div class="row row-1">
		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<u><strong>Christmas Center Senior Coordinator (Full Season)</strong></u>
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Must have strong leadership, management, and organizational skills</li>
					<li>Excellent communication and problem-solving abilities</li>
					<li>Proficient in Word, Excel, and database programs</li>
					<li>Ability to handle stress and manage multiple tasks</li>
					<li>Supervises staff in the&nbsp;absence of the Christmas Services Manager</li>
					<li>Assists with daily operations, client registration, and other assigned tasks</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<u><strong>Bi-Lingual Communication Coordinator (Full Season)</strong></u>
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Must be fluent in Spanish and English</li>
					<li>Provides translation support and communication with Hispanic clients</li>
					<li>Assists with volunteer coordination and registration tasks</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row row-2">
		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<u><strong>Volunteer Coordinator (Full Season)</strong></u>
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Outgoing personality; comfortable speaking to large groups</li>
					<li>Strong communication and organizational skills</li>
					<li>Proficient in online database programs</li>
					<li>Responsible for scheduling, training, and supervising volunteers</li>
					<li>Supports client registration and additional seasonal tasks</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<u><strong>Warehouse Coordinator (Full Season)</strong></u>
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Maintains cleanliness, organization, and inventory of the Christmas Center</li>
					<li>Manages deliveries, recycling, and overall facility upkeep</li>
					<li>Supports traffic flow and parking during registration and distribution</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row row-3">
		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<u><strong>Donor / Special Handling Coordinator (Full Season)</strong></u>
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Strong computer and organizational skills, must have strong excel skills</li>
					<li>Manages donor communication and Angel Tree assignments</li>
					<li>Coordinates preparation and pick-up of Angel orders</li>
					<li>Oversees check-in and placement of special handling items</li>
					<li>Supports client registration as needed</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<u><strong>Toyland Coordinator (Full Season)</strong></u>
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Manages toy inventory and setup of Toyland area</li>
					<li>Organizes toy donations and tracks in-kind contributions</li>
					<li>Oversees volunteers working in Toyland and supports client registration</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:6:25"></div>
